      • setEventStatus

        void setEventStatus​(EventStatus status)
        Sets the EventStatus for this job. The status of the corresponding job to this activity will be set to SUCCESS, WARNING or ERROR likewise. For INFO only the eventStatus will be set, but the job status will stay the same.
        Parameters:
        status - eventStatus to set.

      • setActivityError

        void setActivityError​(ErrorEvent errorEvent)
        Records that an error occurred when executing this activity instance. Whether or not an according event is generated depends on the "njams.sdk.logAllErrors" setting, or the job's end status reported by the executing engine.
        Parameters:
        errorEvent - Information about the error that occurred. This information is used for generating an according event if required.
